{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a contact form that sends the information to support@rubicongamesupplies.com
    
    This is my current artist program submission form. Duplicate this.
    
    
    Name*
    How should we address you?
    Email*
    example@example.com
    Portfolio (web)*
    Link to a portfolio of your work (e.g., ArtStation, Deviant Art, Google Drive)
    How many art pieces would you initially submit (maximum 10)?*
    You can submit a minimum of 1 and a maximum of 10. Note: submitting more doesn't mean they will all get approved.
    How did you hear about our Artist Program?*
    
    All artwork must fit specific guidelines, like resolution (DPI), size, bleed margins, and so on. We provide guidance on sizing for you, but you must properly size it on your own. Are you capable of doing this?*
    
    
    Artist Program Terms & Conditions
    
    Welcome to the Rubicon Artist Program. By submitting your artwork, you agree to the following terms. This summary is designed to be easy to understand.
    
    Ownership & Rights
    
    You retain full ownership of your artwork.
    By submitting, you grant Rubicon a non-exclusive license to use your art on products like playmats, mousepads, and desk mats.
    We may resize or format your artwork to fit printing specifications, but we will not alter its core appearance.
    Commission & Payment
    
    You earn 25% of the net sale price for each product sold featuring your artwork.
    Payments are made quarterly via PayPal or Venmo.
    You may request a sales report at any time.
    Submission Guidelines
    
    You may submit up to 10 designs per calendar quarter.
    Send artwork via our upload portal or email it to: support@rubicongamesupplies.com
    Subject line: “Artist Submission – [Your Name]”
    Revoking Permission
    
    You may revoke your license at any time by emailing us.
    We will stop selling new products with your artwork within 14 business days.
    You will continue to earn commissions on any remaining inventory sold.
    Legal Protections
    
    You confirm that your artwork is original and does not infringe on anyone else’s rights.
    If a third party claims your a, Make each field editable.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-artist-form-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: {{ block.settings.form_padding }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.border_radius }}px;
  }

  .ai-artist-form__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
    margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size }}px;
  }

  .ai-artist-form__subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    margin: 0 0 32px 0;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.subheading_size }}px;
  }

  .ai-artist-form__content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .ai-artist-form__field-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .ai-artist-form__label-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.label_color }};
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.label_size }}px;
  }

  .ai-artist-form__required-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.required_color }};
  }

  .ai-artist-form__help-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.help_text_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.help_text_size }}px;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .ai-artist-form__input-{{ ai_gen_id }},
  .ai-artist-form__textarea-{{ ai_gen_id }},
  .ai-artist-form__select-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    border: {{ block.settings.input_border_width }}px solid {{ block.settings.input_border_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.input_border_radius }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.input_background }};
    color: {{ block.settings.input_text_color }};
    font-size: 14px;
    font-family: inherit;
  }

  .ai-artist-form__input-{{ ai_gen_id }}::placeholder,
  .ai-artist-form__textarea-{{ ai_gen_id }}::placeholder {
    color: {{ block.settings.placeholder_color }};
  }

  .ai-artist-form__input-{{ ai_gen_id }}:focus,
  .ai-artist-form__textarea-{{ ai_gen_id }}:focus,
  .ai-artist-form__select-{{ ai_gen_id }}:focus {
    outline: 2px solid {{ block.settings.focus_color }};
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .ai-artist-form__textarea-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    min-height: 120px;
    resize: vertical;
  }

  .ai-artist-form__select-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .ai-artist-form__radio-group-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .ai-artist-form__radio-option-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .ai-artist-form__radio-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-top: 2px;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .ai-artist-form__radio-label-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .ai-artist-form__terms-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.terms_background }};
    border: 1px solid {{ block.settings.terms_border_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.input_border_radius }}px;
    padding: 20px;
    max-height: 300px;
    overflow-y: auto;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .ai-artist-form__terms-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
  }

  .ai-artist-form__terms-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .ai-artist-form__terms-section-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.label_color }};
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 8px 0;
  }

  .ai-artist-form__terms-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 8px 0;
  }

  .ai-artist-form__checkbox-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 16px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.checkbox_background }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.input_border_radius }}px;
  }

  .ai-artist-form__checkbox-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-top: 2px;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .ai-artist-form__checkbox-label-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .ai-artist-form__button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 16px 32px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_background }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_text_color }};
    border: none;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.button_border_radius }}px;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-artist-form__button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_background }};
  }

  .ai-artist-form__button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:disabled {
    opacity: 0.5;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }

  .ai-artist-form__success-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 16px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.success_background }};
    color: {{ block.settings.success_text_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.input_border_radius }}px;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  .ai-artist-form__error-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 16px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.error_background }};
    color: {{ block.settings.error_text_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.input_border_radius }}px;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-artist-form-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.form_padding | times: 0.6 }}px;
    }

    .ai-artist-form__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size | times: 0.8 }}px;
    }

    .ai-artist-form__subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.subheading_size | times: 0.9 }}px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<div
  class="ai-artist-form-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
  {{ block.shopify_attributes }}
>
  {%- if block.settings.heading != blank -%}
    <h2 class="ai-artist-form__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.heading }}</h2>
  {%- endif -%}

  {%- if block.settings.subheading != blank -%}
    <div class="ai-artist-form__subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.subheading }}</div>
  {%- endif -%}

  {%- form 'contact', id: 'artist-program-form' -%}
    <input
      type="hidden"
      name="contact[form_type]"
      value="artist_program"
    >
    <input
      type="hidden"
      name="contact[email_to]"
      value="{{ block.settings.recipient_email }}"
    >

    <div class="ai-artist-form__content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {%- if block.settings.show_name_field -%}
        <div class="ai-artist-form__field-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <label
            for="artist-name-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            class="ai-artist-form__label-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
          >
            {{ block.settings.name_label }}{%- if block.settings.name_required -%}<span class="ai-artist-form__required-{{ ai_gen_id }}">*</span>{%- endif -%}
          </label>
          <input
            type="text"
            id="artist-name-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            name="contact[name]"
            class="ai-artist-form__input-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            placeholder="{{ block.settings.name_placeholder }}"
            {% if block.settings.name_required %}required aria-required="true"{% endif %}
          >
          {%- if block.settings.name_help_text != blank -%}
            <div class="ai-artist-form__help-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ block.settings.name_help_text }}
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- if block.settings.show_email_field -%}
        <div class="ai-artist-form__field-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <label
            for="artist-email-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            class="ai-artist-form__label-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
          >
            {{ block.settings.email_label }}{%- if block.settings.email_required -%}<span class="ai-artist-form__required-{{ ai_gen_id }}">*</span>{%- endif -%}
          </label>
          <input
            type="email"
            id="artist-email-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            name="contact[email]"
            class="ai-artist-form__input-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            placeholder="{{ block.settings.email_placeholder }}"
            {% if block.settings.email_required %}required aria-required="true"{% endif %}
            autocomplete="email"
          >
          {%- if block.settings.email_help_text != blank -%}
            <div class="ai-artist-form__help-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ block.settings.email_help_text }}
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- if block.settings.show_portfolio_field -%}
        <div class="ai-artist-form__field-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <label
            for="artist-portfolio-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            class="ai-artist-form__label-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
          >
            {{ block.settings.portfolio_label }}{%- if block.settings.portfolio_required -%}<span class="ai-artist-form__required-{{ ai_gen_id }}">*</span>{%- endif -%}
          </label>
          <input
            type="url"
            id="artist-portfolio-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            name="contact[portfolio_url]"
            class="ai-artist-form__input-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            placeholder="{{ block.settings.portfolio_placeholder }}"
            {% if block.settings.portfolio_required %}required aria-required="true"{% endif %}
          >
          {%- if block.settings.portfolio_help_text != blank -%}
            <div class="ai-artist-form__help-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ block.settings.portfolio_help_text }}
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- if block.settings.show_pieces_field -%}
        <div class="ai-artist-form__field-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <label
            for="artist-pieces-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            class="ai-artist-form__label-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
          >
            {{ block.settings.pieces_label }}{%- if block.settings.pieces_required -%}<span class="ai-artist-form__required-{{ ai_gen_id }}">*</span>{%- endif -%}
          </label>
          <select
            id="artist-pieces-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            name="contact[initial_pieces]"
            class="ai-artist-form__select-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            {% if block.settings.pieces_required %}required aria-required="true"{% endif %}
          >
            <option value="">{{ block.settings.pieces_placeholder }}</option>
            {% for i in (1..10) %}
              <option value="{{ i }}">{{ i }}</option>
            {% endfor %}
          </select>
          {%- if block.settings.pieces_help_text != blank -%}
            <div class="ai-artist-form__help-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ block.settings.pieces_help_text }}
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- if block.settings.show_hear_about_field -%}
        <div class="ai-artist-form__field-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <label
            for="artist-hear-about-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            class="ai-artist-form__label-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
          >
            {{ block.settings.hear_about_label }}{%- if block.settings.hear_about_required -%}<span class="ai-artist-form__required-{{ ai_gen_id }}">*</span>{%- endif -%}
          </label>
          <textarea
            id="artist-hear-about-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            name="contact[how_heard]"
            class="ai-artist-form__textarea-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            placeholder="{{ block.settings.hear_about_placeholder }}"
            {% if block.settings.hear_about_required %}required aria-required="true"{% endif %}
          ></textarea>
          {%- if block.settings.hear_about_help_text != blank -%}
            <div class="ai-artist-form__help-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ block.settings.hear_about_help_text }}
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- if block.settings.show_capable_field -%}
        <div class="ai-artist-form__field-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <label class="ai-artist-form__label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ block.settings.capable_label }}{%- if block.settings.capable_required -%}<span class="ai-artist-form__required-{{ ai_gen_id }}">*</span>{%- endif -%}
          </label>
          <div class="ai-artist-form__radio-group-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <div class="ai-artist-form__radio-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <input
                type="radio"
                id="artist-capable-yes-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                name="contact[capable_sizing]"
                value="Yes"
                class="ai-artist-form__radio-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                {% if block.settings.capable_required %}required aria-required="true"{% endif %}
              >
              <label
                for="artist-capable-yes-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                class="ai-artist-form__radio-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              >
                {{ block.settings.capable_yes_label }}
              </label>
            </div>
            <div class="ai-artist-form__radio-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <input
                type="radio"
                id="artist-capable-no-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                name="contact[capable_sizing]"
                value="No"
                class="ai-artist-form__radio-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              >
              <label
                for="artist-capable-no-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                class="ai-artist-form__radio-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              >
                {{ block.settings.capable_no_label }}
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>
          {%- if block.settings.capable_help_text != blank -%}
            <div class="ai-artist-form__help-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ block.settings.capable_help_text }}
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- if block.settings.show_terms -%}
        <div class="ai-artist-form__terms-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {%- if block.settings.terms_heading != blank -%}
            <h3 class="ai-artist-form__terms-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.terms_heading }}</h3>
          {%- endif -%}
          {%- if block.settings.terms_intro != blank -%}
            <p class="ai-artist-form__terms-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ block.settings.terms_intro }}
            </p>
          {%- endif -%}

          {%- if block.settings.terms_section_1_heading != blank -%}
            <div class="ai-artist-form__terms-section-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <h4 class="ai-artist-form__terms-section-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.terms_section_1_heading }}</h4>
              {%- if block.settings.terms_section_1_content != blank -%}
                <div class="ai-artist-form__terms-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {{ block.settings.terms_section_1_content }}
                </div>
              {%- endif -%}
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}

          {%- if block.settings.terms_section_2_heading != blank -%}
            <div class="ai-artist-form__terms-section-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <h4 class="ai-artist-form__terms-section-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.terms_section_2_heading }}</h4>
              {%- if block.settings.terms_section_2_content != blank -%}
                <div class="ai-artist-form__terms-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {{ block.settings.terms_section_2_content }}
                </div>
              {%- endif -%}
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}

          {%- if block.settings.terms_section_3_heading != blank -%}
            <div class="ai-artist-form__terms-section-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <h4 class="ai-artist-form__terms-section-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.terms_section_3_heading }}</h4>
              {%- if block.settings.terms_section_3_content != blank -%}
                <div class="ai-artist-form__terms-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {{ block.settings.terms_section_3_content }}
                </div>
              {%- endif -%}
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}

          {%- if block.settings.terms_section_4_heading != blank -%}
            <div class="ai-artist-form__terms-section-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <h4 class="ai-artist-form__terms-section-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.terms_section_4_heading }}</h4>
              {%- if block.settings.terms_section_4_content != blank -%}
                <div class="ai-artist-form__terms-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {{ block.settings.terms_section_4_content }}
                </div>
              {%- endif -%}
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}

          {%- if block.settings.terms_section_5_heading != blank -%}
            <div class="ai-artist-form__terms-section-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <h4 class="ai-artist-form__terms-section-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.terms_section_5_heading }}</h4>
              {%- if block.settings.terms_section_5_content != blank -%}
                <div class="ai-artist-form__terms-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {{ block.settings.terms_section_5_content }}
                </div>
              {%- endif -%}
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>

        <div class="ai-artist-form__checkbox-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <input
            type="checkbox"
            id="artist-terms-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            name="contact[terms_accepted]"
            value="Yes"
            class="ai-artist-form__checkbox-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            required
            aria-required="true"
          >
          <label
            for="artist-terms-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            class="ai-artist-form__checkbox-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
          >
            {{ block.settings.terms_checkbox_label }}<span class="ai-artist-form__required-{{ ai_gen_id }}">*</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}

      <button
        type="submit"
        class="ai-artist-form__button-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
      >
        {{ block.settings.button_text }}
      </button>

      {%- if form.posted_successfully? -%}
        <div
          class="ai-artist-form__success-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
          role="status"
        >
          {{ block.settings.success_message }}
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- if form.errors -%}
        <div
          class="ai-artist-form__error-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
          role="alert"
        >
          {{ form.errors | default_errors }}
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}
    </div>
  {%- endform -%}
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Artist program form",
  "tag": null,
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Form content"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "heading",
      "label": "Heading",
      "default": "Artist Program Application"
    },
    {
      "type": "textarea",
      "id": "subheading",
      "label": "Subheading",
      "default": "Join our community of talented artists and showcase your work on our products."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "recipient_email",
      "label": "Recipient email",
      "default": "support@rubicongamesupplies.com"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "button_text",
      "label": "Button text",
      "default": "Submit Application"
    },
    {
      "type": "textarea",
      "id": "success_message",
      "label": "Success message",
      "default": "Thank you for your submission! We'll review your application and get back to you soon."
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Name field"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "show_name_field",
      "label": "Show name field",
      "default": true
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "name_label",
      "label": "Label",
      "default": "Name"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "name_placeholder",
      "label": "Placeholder",
      "default": "How should we address you?"
    },
    {
      "type": "textarea",
      "id": "name_help_text",
      "label": "Help text"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "name_required",
      "label": "Required",
      "default": true
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Email field"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "show_email_field",
      "label": "Show email field",
      "default": true
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "email_label",
      "label": "Label",
      "default": "Email"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "email_placeholder",
      "label": "Placeholder",
      "default": "example@example.com"
    },
    {
      "type": "textarea",
      "id": "email_help_text",
      "label": "Help text"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "email_required",
      "label": "Required",
      "default": true
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Portfolio field"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "show_portfolio_field",
      "label": "Show portfolio field",
      "default": true
